item.description: Join Barbara Moura for a FREE Intro to Angel Card Reading for Beginners and learn how to pull and read Angel Cards for you and your closest friends and family! Barbara Moura, AHP (Angel Healing Practitioner) has been working with the angels for longer than she can remember. Receiving her certification in June of 2006 as an Angel Card Reader, Barbara and enjoys sharing the insightful messages from the angels with anyone that has an interest. In this intro, gain insight into who the Angels are, how to choose, connect and read Angel Cards, what other props and tools you can use to enhance your readings and enjoy a sample reading from Barbara herself! If you have always wanted to learn how to pull and read Angel Cards, then this class is for you!
